OL,6,FHe described his time in prison as
OL,7,Flife-altering, adding that even the
OL,8,Fprobation service had recommended a
OL,9,Fsuspended sentence ` but the Post
OL,10,FOffice had insisted on a custodial
OL,11,Fterm.
OL,13,F"It leaves a mark," he said.
OL,15,FTuesday's 162-page report also
OL,16,Fconcluded Post Office bosses knew the
OL,17,FHorizon IT system had widespread
OL,18,Ffaults, but had "maintained the
OL,19,Ffiction" it was accurate for years.
