OL,3,C'It ruined people's lives': Post
OL,4,COffice Horizon scandal report published
OL,6,FResponding to the report, Post Office
OL,7,FMinister Gareth Thomas said he has a
OL,8,F"considerable amount of sympathy" for
OL,9,Finquiry chairman Sir Wyn Williams's
OL,10,Frecommendation of a standing public
OL,11,Fbody to deliver redress in future
OL,12,Fscandals.
OL,14,FHe also said: "We have put in place an
OL,15,Fappeals process to try to give those
OL,16,Fwho feel that they have not received
OL,17,Fto date a fair offer the chance to get
OL,18,Ffull and fair redress."
