OL,3,C'It ruined people's lives': Post
OL,4,COffice Horizon scandal report published
OL,6,FThe report estimates that up to 10,000
OL,7,Fpeople may have been affected by the
OL,8,FHorizon scandal, including those
OL,9,Fwrongfully convicted and others who
OL,10,Fsuffered financial loss or
OL,11,Freputational damage due to the
OL,12,Fsystem's failures.
OL,14,FAmong its findings, the report sets
OL,15,Fout 19 recommendations. One key
OL,16,Fproposal from Sir Wyn Williams calls
OL,17,Ffor a formal process to compensate the
OL,18,Ffamilies of those harmed by the
OL,19,Fscandal.
