OL,3,C'It ruined people's lives': Post
OL,4,COffice Horizon scandal report published
OL,6,FSir Wyn said: "I readily accept that
OL,7,Feven if my recommendations are
OL,8,Faccepted and implemented as quickly as
OL,9,FI would like, they will not constitute
OL,10,Fsome magic formula for removing all of
OL,11,Fthe problems from which the schemes
OL,12,Fsuffer.
OL,14,F"As my report makes clear, I am
OL,15,Fcritical of the Post Office and the
OL,16,FDepartment (of Business and Trade) in
OL,17,Frelation to the development and
OL,18,Fevolution of these schemes in a number
OL,19,Fof important respects ` not least in
OL,20,Frelation to some of the egregious
OL,21,Fdelays which have occurred."
